My understanding is that the chatbot in the TCM project is designed for stu=
dents' independent learning (mainly speaking practice), allowing them to in=
teract and simulate conversations with English-speaking patients and collea=
gues. The clinical scenarios, principles of effective TCM communication, an=
d sample dialogues have been shared with Simon and his team in July (see at=
tached emails). Since the chatbot is intended for self-directed learning an=
d practice, I do not think it is necessary to develop formal lesson plans.

